# oneinfra

`oneinfra` is a Kubernetes as a Service platform. It empowers you to
provide or consume Kubernetes clusters at scale, on any platform or
service provider. You decide.

|                                               |                                                     |
|-----------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------|
